Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:04.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Muncește din greu, dragul meu \Ncandidat pentru Mesia...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.51,0:00:06.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Poți face orice dacă încerci.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.22,0:00:09.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eu te voi susține din umbră!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.02,0:00:12.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Îngerii sunt ființe răbdătoare.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.27,0:00:15.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eu sunt îngerul stăruinței, Uriel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.70,0:00:17.70,KazuyaShuuSign,,0,0,0,,Stăruință
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.02,0:00:18.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,M-am camuflat în umbre ca să-mi sprijin candidatul pentru Mesia,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.49,0:00:21.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,și să nu fiu descoperită de cei loiali Diavolului.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.82,0:00:25.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While I lie in the Messiah Candidate's shadow,\NI patiently endure even my need to relieve myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.71,0:00:27.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I disappear into the shadows so others will not see me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.04,0:00:29.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.63,0:00:31.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pretend you don't see her, pretend you don't see her...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.37,0:00:33.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be patient...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.77,0:00:35.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be patient...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.79,0:00:37.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please strive hard at work!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.55,0:00:40.89,KazuyaShuuSign,,0,0,0,,Episodul 2\N Te susțin din umbră
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.71,0:00:40.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Seven Heavenly Virtues!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.47,0:00:45.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O Candidate for Messiah,\Nyou will soon be at the station...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.68,0:00:48.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You must be patient a little while longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.65,0:00:53.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good luck at work today, O Candidate for Messiah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.08,0:00:55.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have warmed your change of clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.61,0:00:58.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just... ten more minutes until your lunch break.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.58,0:00:59.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be patient!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.57,0:01:02.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...the hell is this? A letter on an arrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.62,0:01:06.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have fallen in love with you,\NO Candidate for Messiah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.25,0:01:10.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, I must humbly report that your exhaustion\Nis beginning to show upon your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.63,0:01:13.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Humbly report"?\NWhy is she following me around in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.80,0:01:15.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't focus on my work.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.63,0:01:17.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps my support has been lacking,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.84,0:01:21.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,as for the last few days, the Messiah Candidate's\Nwork performance has plummeted rapidly...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.60,0:01:23.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a fierce battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.72,0:01:25.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I no longer have any time to waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.64,0:01:28.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I am to train him to be a wonderful Messiah,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.69,0:01:31.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I must offer him even more support from the shadows!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.24,0:01:41.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today's a really important day for work.\NHow long's she gonna follow me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.94,0:01:44.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am extremely delighted to receive your praise.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.24,0:01:49.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am Uriel, the Angel who patiently endures.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.87,0:01:53.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to support the Messiah Candidate\Nto raise his work performance,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.50,0:01:58.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I must always hide myself so none discover my existence\Nand patiently endure through the days.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.13,0:02:01.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if I must squeeze between walls...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.13,0:02:04.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hot...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.30,0:02:06.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I must be patient...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.89,0:02:09.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I say something, I will interrupt his dinner...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.43,0:02:13.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.31,0:02:16.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is {\i1}that{\i0} the reason your performance's\Ndone a nosedive?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.11,0:02:20.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No, she's got nothing to do with it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.82,0:02:22.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been seen...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.67,0:02:25.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the Messiah Candidate protected me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.11,0:02:31.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I must endure my urge to urinate\Nso as to not interrupt his work day...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.54,0:02:35.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I must endure... must endure...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.96,0:02:38.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,E-Endure...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.82,0:02:40.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Endure...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.05,0:02:41.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will endure!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.55,0:02:45.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.39,0:02:49.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But... because I didn't know\Nwhere the restroom was, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.77,0:02:51.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I can't just leave you alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.90,0:02:54.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am seriously reflecting upon my actions!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.40,0:02:56.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be it drawn and quartering, or parading me\Nthrough town to the gallows,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.69,0:02:58.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you may do as you wish with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.44,0:02:59.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whoa, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.90,0:03:03.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the end, the Messiah Candidate was fired...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.86,0:03:10.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looking for a new job ain't easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.41,0:03:11.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:13.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.00,0:03:14.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're home so early!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.92,0:03:17.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was just going to hide myself...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.42,0:03:20.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With that sheet? And why are you here anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.88,0:03:22.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.79,0:03:26.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was going to support your job search\Nfrom the shadows...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.88,0:03:28.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In any case, I hope...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.93,0:03:31.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...you will treat me kindly from now on!
